React To-Do List App

A simple To-Do List application built with React. It allows users to add and delete tasks with an interactive user interface.

Features:
- Add new tasks
- Delete existing tasks
- Checkbox (UI only — can be extended to mark tasks complete)

Project Structure:
src/
│
├── App.jsx
├── App.css
├── components/
│   ├── InputContainer.jsx
│   ├── TodoContainer.jsx
│   └── Todo.jsx

How to Run:
1. Clone the repository
   git clone <your-repo-url>
   cd your-repo-folder

2. Install dependencies
   npm install

3. Start the development server
   npm run dev

4. Open in browser
   Visit http://localhost:xxxx to view the app

Future Improvements:
- Mark tasks as completed
- Edit existing tasks
- Persist tasks using local storage or backend

Made with React
